Package: autoSTK
Type: Package
Title: Automatic spatio-temporal kriging functionality for automap package
Version: 1.0.2
Author: Insang Song
Maintainer: Insang Song <sigmafelix@hotmail.com>
Description: Automatic spatio-temporal Kriging 
    This package offers several functions to fit spatio-temporal variograms in terms of minimal SSE. Some candidate models are applied in default, and users can choose what theoretical models will be applied. Four cross-validation strategies for spatiotemporal data are implemented.
